<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">There is hope for the suffering in the knowledge that God never leaves you. There is nowhere anywhere in existence that we can escape from God or be separated from Him. Who better to trust with our lives and our souls, who better to suffer next to than the one who is always directly near us and knows everything we are going through at a personal level?</p></body></html>